item.title: 【Music Videos】Madonna & Sickick - Frozen On Fire [4K VP9 | PCM 24-bit 88.2 kHz | DD+ Dolby Atmos]
item.description:
Genre: Electronic, Pop
Style: Downtempo, Trap
Year: 2021 (Remix), Original song: 1998
Video Source: YouTube 2160p (not available on a better streaming source)
Audio Source: Qobuz & Apple Music (Atmos Mix), thanks to moi & SonMaxime

"Frozen On Fire " is a remix project by Madonna in collaboration with Canadian DJ, singer, vocalist, producer and beatboxer Sickick. It's a remix of "Frozen", a song from her seventh studio album, Ray of Light (1998). "Frozen" was written by Madonna and Patrick Leonard, who both produced it in collaboration with William Orbit. The downtempo electronica ballad, which has a layered sound enhanced by synthesizers and strings, lyrically addresses a cold and emotionless man.

In 2021, a Chill-Trap remix of "Frozen", made by Canadian DJ Sickick, became viral on TikTok. On December 3, 2021, it was officially released as the first single from Madonna's entire-catalog reissue project. Madonna and Sickick released three further renditions of the remix; a version featuring Nigerian singer Fireboy DML, a version featuring American rapper 070 Shake, and the version featuring vocals from Sickick himself titled "Frozen on Fire". Madonna even went into the studio with Sickick to re-record her vocals and sing a completely new verse. Madonna said: "I was jealous that so many other people sang along to my track. I wanted to remind everyone that I wrote this song."
The Sickick remix charted within the top ten of the Billboard Dance/Electronic Songs chart, and was certified Gold by the Syndicat National de l'Édition Phonographique (SNEP) in France.

Release Info

The PCM track is downloaded from Qobuz (Hi-Res, 24-bit 88.2 kHz) & synced with Adobe Audition.

The timed lyrics are synced and edited. Enable the subtitles to see the lyrics.
